- Convergent evidence from 5 projects: corrected anti-TNF (epithelial defense genes as top SHAP), stricture risk (CPA3/EMT/collagen), IL-23 atlas (4.8% epithelial cells), microbiome subtypes (Paneth defensins → microbial community), fibrosis (EMT/SERPINE1/GREM1)
