### Critical Update: Ferroptosis Initiative Rationale Weakened

**cd-gpx4-ferroptosis-convergence** downgraded from ★★★★ to ★★★.
- Corrected anti-TNF eliminated GSDMC, NFS1, ACAD9 — all leakage artifacts
- Anti-TNF convergence pillar definitively invalidated
- Surviving pillars: external literature (Verstockt GPX4/post-op), IL-23 atlas ILC2 ferroptosis, flare prediction metabolic stress
- CASP6 (apoptosis) survives in corrected model, shifting regulated cell death from ferroptosis → apoptosis
- Do not pause — GPX4 scRNA-seq landscape and literature validation still worthwhile

